With shifting eyes but eyebrows still raised, Telydnin handed him the purse. 
"Yes, it's a nice purse. Yes, yes," he said, grow- ing suddenly pale, and added, "Look at it, young man." 
Rost6v took the purse in his hand, examined it and the money in it, and looked at Telydnin. The lieutenant was looking about in his usual way and suddenly seemed to grow very merry.
